reviews.review_text:
Civic Cneter I remember these show well. They played a smaller place than normal (the Rectum was where they usually played). It seemed a little more intimate. The three night run was pretty standard for '85.

I remember taking purple micro-dots as well as having a purple ticket (tour booklet) and parking on the purple level this night. It was a purple night to say the least!!
civic center my best friend was going to penn at this time and we partied at the frat house before and walked to the show had a shroomin time !
